TITLE 'Simple diffusion equation'

{ this problem lacks sources and boundary conditions }

VARIABLES        

u

DEFINITIONS

k=3        { conductivity }

EQUATIONS

div(k*grad(u)) =0

BOUNDARIES

REGION 1

    START(0,0)

VALUE(u) = 0        LINE TO (9,0)        { fixed value on bottom }

NATURAL(u)=15        LINE TO (9,7)        { insulated right side }

VALUE(u)=1                LINE TO (0,7)        { fixed value on top }

NATURAL(u)=0        LINE TO CLOSE        { insulated left side }

PLOTS

CONTOUR(u)

VECTOR(k*grad(u))

END